<p>Not to recommend a tote other than <a href="https://lithub.com/we-need-your-help-support-lit-hub-become-a-member/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Tote</a>, but anecdotal evidence suggests that an inordinate number of writers were once (&#8220;once&#8221;) Richard Scarry fans. If they&#8217;ve got kids now, even better.</p>
