<h3><strong><a href="https://naadam.co/products/lofty-cashmere-blanket?variant=41184391266400" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Cashmere Blanket</a>, $378</strong></h3>
<p>Here&#8217;s a free hack: Sometimes when you&#8217;re so comfortable that you don&#8217;t want to get up, the only thing to do is to keep writing. Besides, everyone loves cashmere.</p>
<p><a href="https://store.moma.org/products/fenestra-bookends-set-of-4" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263609" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/153302_a_1296x-copy/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy.jpg" data-orig-size="1296,1102" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="153302_a_1296x copy" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-300x255.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-1204x1024.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-263609" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="425" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy.jpg 1296w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-300x255.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-1204x1024.jpg 1204w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-768x653.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-60x51.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/153302_a_1296x-copy-50x43.jpg 50w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></a></p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://store.moma.org/products/fenestra-bookends-set-of-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Fenestra Bookends</a>, $75</strong></h2>
<p>Writers tend to have too many books. We wouldn&#8217;t recommend going whole hog and buying someone a bookcase (unless you know them extremely well), but these bookends could certainly help.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.ndbooks.com/shop/product/new-classics-club/" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263613" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1.avif" data-orig-size="523,250" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256&#215;600" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1-300x143.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1.avif" class="aligncenter wp-image-263613" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1.avif" alt="" width="500" height="239" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1.avif 523w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1-300x143.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1-60x29.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/9843e5ac38b0cc0054fb35dc87e57d9a766576e1-1256x600-1-50x24.jpg 50w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></a></p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://www.ndbooks.com/shop/product/new-classics-club/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">New Directions New Classics Club</a>, $175</strong></h2>
<p>We said no books, and this is books, but more importantly, it&#8217;s a way of life. Plus, reading a year&#8217;s worth of offerings from New Directions would make pretty much anyone a better writer.</p>
<p><a href="https://shop.scholastic.com/parent-ecommerce/books/animorphs-retro-tin-set-9781338678833.html" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263624" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/700-2/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1.jpg" data-orig-size="690,541" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="700" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1-300x235.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-263624" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="392" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1.jpg 690w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1-300x235.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1-60x47.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/700-1-50x39.jpg 50w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></a></p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://shop.scholastic.com/parent-ecommerce/books/animorphs-retro-tin-set-9781338678833.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Animorphs Retro Tin Set</a>, $35</strong></h2>
<p>Okay, okay, this is also books, but not really, because it&#8217;s all about the nostalgia, and no one loves nostalgia more than writers. Many of a certain age will have fond memories of these books (the commemorative tin box comes with books 1-6). There&#8217;s also <em><a href="https://shop.scholastic.com/parent-ecommerce/books/goosebumps-retro-terror-set-9781546164135.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Goosebumps</a>Â </em>andÂ <a href="https://shop.scholastic.com/parent-ecommerce/books/the-baby-sitters-club-retro-tin-boxed-set-9781338311488.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Baby-Sitters Club</em></a>, depending on your personal writer&#8217;s vibe.</p>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/gift_cards" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263602" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy.jpg" data-orig-size="1000,599" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f copy" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy-300x180.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-263602" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/sweater-gift-card-2025-static-no-snow-no-shadow-199af8e78d8bb9d47808ccc106e45870d648193f04c800d9d9ea0609255f650f-copy.jp