<h2><strong><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/gift_cards" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Bookshop.org Gift Card</a>, $?</strong></h2>
<p>You can solve the problem of buying-or-not-buying books for writers completely, however, by simply letting them choose for themselves. No doubt they have a wishlist a mile long.</p>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263603" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/lhbooks-copy/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy.jpg" data-orig-size="831,804" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="LHbooks copy" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy-300x290.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-263603" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="484" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy.jpg 831w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy-300x290.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy-768x743.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy-60x58.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LHbooks-copy-50x48.jpg 50w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></a></p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://bookshop.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Bookshop.org Receipt</a>, $??</strong></h2>
<p>Actually, here&#8217;s an even better idea: give your favorite writer a receipt. That&#8217;s right. The receipt should clearly show that you&#8217;ve recently published a whole stack of said favorite writer&#8217;s books, which you will be gifting to the rest of your friends and family. It&#8217;s the gift that keeps on etc.</p>
