<h2><strong><a href="https://lithub.memberful.com/join" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">A Year of Literary Hub Membership</a>, $70</strong></h2>
<p>Members at the Bibliophile level get our classic Joan Didion tote (not available in stores, be they digital or physical), an ad-free reading experience (!), an exclusive member-only monthly newsletter where we tell you what we&#8217;re really reading, and early access to giveaways of early copies of new books. Well! You could do worse.</p>
