<h2><strong><a href="https://centerforfiction.org/join-give/the-writers-studio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Center for Fiction Writers Studio Membership</a>, $250/month</strong></h2>
<p>Does your favorite NYC-based writer need a room (or at least a desk) of their own, and more importantly, do they want to be involved in more <a href="https://www.curbed.com/article/novelist-drama-desk-fight-space-brooklyn-center-for-fiction.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">DRAMA</a> in the new year? Snag them a coveted spot at the Center for Fiction&#8230;if you can.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.care.com/" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263606" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-literary-hub-gift-guide-50-gifts-for-writers/different-toys-on-pink-background-flat-lay/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/AdobeStock_401099113-scaled.jpeg" data-orig-size="2560,1707" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;9&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;New Africa - stock.adobe.com&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark III&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Different toys on pink background, flat lay&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1594715352&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;Olga Yastremska, New Africa, Africa Studio&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;70&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Different toys on pink background, flat lay&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Different toys on pink background, flat lay" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Different toys on pink background, flat lay&lt;/p&gt;
