<h2><strong><a href="https://www.care.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Childcare</a>, $????</strong></h2>
<p>Let&#8217;s be honest, though. What the writer in your life <em>really</em> needs is simple: more time. If they have children, they probably have even less than you imagine. Consider, this holiday season, supporting your local writer with a recurring childcare fund (or recurring childcare duties). This is a sure way to get yourself thanked in the next book.</p>
